The paper is about federated learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The dataset used in the paper is an image dataset (cs.CV) and the algorithms implemented are object detection algorithms (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the efficiency and communication aspects of federated learning, which are related to distributed computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper involves the use of machine learning models, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
